# JSON-RPC Bridge — See packages/sdk

The full protocol rules (envelope shape, origin validation, how to add a new
method/event) live in `packages/sdk/.cursor/rules/json-rpc-protocol.mdc` —
read that file before changing anything in `ParcelIQEmbed.tsx`.

The one host-specific rule: `ParcelIQEmbed` is the *only* place in this app
allowed to construct a `ParcelIQWidget` or touch its `onMessage` hook. Every
other component should go through the `useLeads`/`useFlagLead` hooks
instead of reaching into the widget directly.
